PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774023076
OL,3,CFamily denies seeking to freeze Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe's social media accounts
OL,6,FOver their three statements it was
OL,7,Festablished that a request had been
OL,8,Fput to tech company Meta that owns
OL,9,FInstagram to memorialise Noah's
OL,10,FInstagram account, which effectively
OL,11,Ffreezes it and retains the information
OL,12,Fin it at that time.
OL,14,FPeter Coll KC, counsel for the
OL,15,Fcoroner, showed the form that was
OL,16,Fsubmitted to Meta on June 28 2020, the
OL,17,Fday after Noah's body was found, with
OL,18,FM1's name and a shared family email
OL,19,Faddress.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774023076
OL,3,CFamily denies seeking to freeze Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe's social media accounts
OL,6,FWhere a proof of death is required, a
OL,7,Flink was inserted to a news article
OL,8,Ffrom the time saying that Noah had
OL,9,Fdied.
OL,11,FM1 said he was a student at St
OL,12,FMalachy's college in June 2020 but he
OL,13,Fdid not know Noah at the time, telling
OL,14,Fthe inquest: "I only realised who he
OL,15,Fwas when I seen his face on a poster."
OL,26,@vD@NOUwD@fO]
