CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774023076
OL,3,CFamily denies seeking to freeze Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe's social media accounts
OL,6,FUnder questioning from Kate Hanley,
OL,7,Fcounsel for Fiona Donohoe, he
OL,8,Freiterated that he did not seek to
OL,9,Fmemorialise Noah's account and said "I
OL,10,Fdo wish I did" when asked if he knew
OL,11,Fwho attempted to.
OL,13,FAsked if he could help any further he
OL,14,Fsaid: "If I could I would, I promise I
OL,15,Fwould say it."
OL,17,FM2 said she also did not know Noah and
OL,18,Fonly became aware of him after his
OL,19,Fdisappearance in June 2020.
OL,26,@qD@eOUrD@NO]vD@GOUwD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
