OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774023076
OL,3,CFamily denies seeking to freeze Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe's social media accounts
OL,6,FBrenda Campbell KC, representing Ms
OL,7,FDonohoe, said that as a result of the
OL,8,Fmemorialisation "the day after she
OL,9,Flearned that her child had died she
OL,10,Fhad no access to any of his private
OL,11,Fsocial media", and Ms Donohoe was
OL,12,F"locked out".
OL,14,FMs Campbell said Ms Donohoe was
OL,15,Fconcerned "someone had done this to
OL,16,Fdeliberately deprive her and us of
OL,17,Fthat access" to Noah's accounts.
OL,19,FM2 confirmed she understood what Ms
OL,20,FCampbell described as that
OL,21,F"significant and serious point".
OL,26,@pD@QOUsD@MO]tD@AOUtD@LO]wD@KOUyD@LO]}D@
OL,26,AAOU}D@_O]
