OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774023076
OL,3,CFamily denies seeking to freeze Noah
OL,4,CDonohoe's social media accounts
OL,6,FM2 said "of course" she would say if
OL,7,Fshe had further information, but that
OL,8,Fshe did not seek to memorialise Noah's
OL,9,Faccount and did not know who did.
OL,11,FHer statement also referenced accounts
OL,12,Fbeing hacked and she told jurors,
OL,13,F"back in 2020 and years like that
OL,14,Fthere was an epidemic of Instagram
OL,15,Faccounts being hacked it was always
OL,16,Fjust scam websites, things like that".
OL,18,FShe added: "I know my brother was
OL,19,Fhacked a few times and my account was
OL,20,Fhacked as well."
OL,26,@nD@IOUnD@SO]uD@AOUxD@eO]zD@LOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
